00:36:37.852 --> 00:36:41.152
done by Tak Mak, you get a more aggressive phenotype than

613
00:36:41.212 --> 00:36:44.752
IDH1 and NPM1 alone, both in primary and

614
00:36:44.972 --> 00:36:48.876
secondary transplants.And importantly, these leukemias

615
00:36:48.936 --> 00:36:52.616
tend to have less expression of more

616
00:36:52.716 --> 00:36:56.636
immature markers, so you tend to get less of what

617
00:36:56.656 --> 00:36:59.516
we would say is a lineage-negative, SCA positive, KIT positive.

