00:37:52.516 --> 00:37:55.486
often get venetoclax azacitidine resistance.

633
00:37:55.486 --> 00:37:59.396
So this myeloid mismaturation state is probably a marker

634
00:37:59.436 --> 00:38:02.396
for lack of sensitivity to some therapies.

635
00:38:02.436 --> 00:38:04.636
Probably not, though, to chemotherapy, I would point out.

636
00:38:05.636 --> 00:38:09.396
And what I will tell you is that if we treat either mouse or

637
00:38:09.516 --> 00:38:13.136
human models with IDH inhibitors, the RAS

638
00:38:13.256 --> 00:38:17.116
wild-type IDH mutant leukemias do differentiate, so

