00:38:17.136 --> 00:38:21.056
they go from having low expression myeloid markers to putting them on.

640
00:38:21.376 --> 00:38:24.936
They lose their early markers like CD3438 double

641
00:38:25.016 --> 00:38:28.596
positivity, whereas the IDH mutated leukemias, which already have

