00:40:43.696 --> 00:40:46.766
So ELOVL1 is one of the enzymes that's a

680
00:40:46.956 --> 00:40:47.816
rate-limiting

681
00:40:48.636 --> 00:40:52.116
enzyme, that whole family, and very long-chain fatty acid

