00:42:54.236 --> 00:42:57.096
rescue the CRISPR dependency, but the catalytic dead do not.

718
00:42:57.176 --> 00:43:01.136
So we know that the catalytic activity of ELOVL1 is required for

719
00:43:01.196 --> 00:43:04.788
this dependency.We then asked if this was unique to

