00:43:08.828 --> 00:43:12.738
ones are at all a dependency, suggesting this is very specific to

722
00:43:12.748 --> 00:43:13.658
ELOVL1.

723
00:43:14.588 --> 00:43:18.248
So conclusions from this first part of two are that we have

724
00:43:18.268 --> 00:43:21.808
genetic and pharmacologic assays that reveal ELOVL1 as a

725
00:43:21.828 --> 00:43:23.728
dependency in NRAS mutant leukemias.

726
00:43:24.248 --> 00:43:27.688
ELOVL1 is not a dependency in wild-type stem cells or in

